gestaltung aus Publikationen »Druckerzeugnisse« macht.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aDifferentiation (Sociology). 0aInvestigative reporting. 0aSocial problems. 4aDifferenzierungstheorie. 4aDigitalisierung. 4aGlobalisierung. 4aIrritation. 4aJournalismus. 4aKonfliktforschung. 4aKorrektur. 4aMedien. 4aOrganisation. 4aPanama Papers. 4aProtest. 4aSoziale Ungleichheit. 4aSoziologie. 4aSoziologische Theorie. 4aSystemtheorie. 4aWissenssoziologie. 4aÜbersetzungstheorie. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Sociology / General.2bisacsh  aConflict Studies.  aCorrection.  aDifferentiation Theory.  aDigitalization.  aGlobalization.  aIrritation.  aJournalism.  aMedia.  aOrganization.  aProtest.  aSocial Inequality.  aSociological Theory.  aSociology of Knowledge.  aSociology.  aSystems Theory.  aTranslation Theory.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2019z978311071956708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019z9783110664232oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Social Sciences 2019z9783110606485oZDB-23-DSW40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839449998zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839449998423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839449998/original  a978-3-11-071956-7  DG Plus eBook-Package 2019b2019  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2019  aZDB-23-DSWb2019